dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents Council Districts Pre-2014 for New Orleans, LA in 2017. This layer represents the Council Districts for the City of New Orleans that were no longer effective as of May 5, 2014. These boundaries changed based on reapportionment following the 2010 Census. This file was downloaded on December, 2018 by NYU Data Services. It was originally represented on the New Orleans Open Data Socrata portal as catalog record rc5i-5hwb
dc_title_s: Council Districts Pre-2014 for New Orleans, LA, 2017
